code: public static GrpcExchangeForwarder createExchangeForwarder(GrpcConfiguration configuration, Object grpcStub) {     if (configuration.getProducerStrategy() == GrpcProducerStrategy.SIMPLE) {         return new GrpcSimpleExchangeForwarder(configuration, grpcStub).     } else if (configuration.getProducerStrategy() == GrpcProducerStrategy.STREAMING) {         return new GrpcStreamingExchangeForwarder(configuration, grpcStub).     } else {         throw new IllegalStateException("Unsupported producer strategy: " + configuration.getProducerStrategy()).     } }
